    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/e29de99715601a7793a41c6df00fddef.avif?t=1771531027\" width=598 height=370 /></span><br>After a game cartridge falls from the sky, you wake up in a strange new world full of big heads, strawberries, manga, and cake!  In this world, there are two sides to every soul: Main and Invert!<br><br>Welcome to Furquest - a cute RPG about loving your friends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/5a7f703cc46004c952bbe12d02e7c51b.avif?t=1771531027\" width=512 height=74 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A cute story about a shaggy dog, a lonely bunny, a goofy horse and a... wolf. becoming best friends!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/386341d9f68b1da8784cfc3517bd86db.apng?t=1771531027\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/386341d9f68b1da8784cfc3517bd86db.poster.avif?t=1771531027\" class=\"bb_img\" width=285 height=144 /></picture></span><br></li><li>Every enemy in Furquest has their own unique minigame for you to play!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/e8c4fcf8b42db36b6d677bbbd250b5c4.apng?t=1771531027\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/e8c4fcf8b42db36b6d677bbbd250b5c4.poster.avif?t=1771531027\" class=\"bb_img\" width=372 height=102 /></picture></span><br></li><li>Tons of games to play in the world - carve pumpkins, decorate snow people, read manga, play basketball + more!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/90228d607d0c9263cae5215ed695740e.apng?t=1771531027\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/90228d607d0c9263cae5215ed695740e.poster.avif?t=1771531027\" class=\"bb_img\" width=96 height=96 /></picture></span><br></li><li>Unique boss fights covering a range of different genres from cooking games to visual novels!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/62a910b438f2eec8b892a3aaf8788101.apng?t=1771531027\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/62a910b438f2eec8b892a3aaf8788101.poster.avif?t=1771531027\" class=\"bb_img\" width=195 height=192 /></picture></span><br></li><li>A sweet art style and a sour soundtrack!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/f3681528f02eeb7bcf5c36b150ae680c.apng?t=1771531027\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/f3681528f02eeb7bcf5c36b150ae680c.poster.avif?t=1771531027\" class=\"bb_img\" width=147 height=81 /></picture></span></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/e199d97ffefba5b639fbb998342611d6.avif?t=1771531027\" width=512 height=74 /></span><br><i>In this world, there are two sides to every coin.  Although, while that is also true for your world...<br><br>In this world, there are two sides to every soul: MAIN and INVERT.  A 'good' Main will be matched by an 'evil' Invert.  A 'happy' Main will be matched by an 'unhappy' Invert, and so on.<br><br>However...<br><br>By stealing the other's soul, the soul thief will transform into an incredibly powerful new form, a HERO SOUL!<br><br>After X,000 years of Soul Wars, Prince Aef has made friendship itself a crime as a last ditch effort to separate the groups and protect their souls.<br><br>One fateful day, a rather strange puppy wakes up in this world. This is their story... er, quest!</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740230/extras/e4c902e1167fd173c49d1bb2f986cdc0.avif?t=1771531027\" width=396 height=170 /></span>",
